message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs and expectations. This exceptional item is valued at $12000 by us due to its unique features and high-quality craftsmanship. We believe it could be an invaluable asset to you, potentially increasing your productivity and satisfaction. Considering its worth and the benefits it offers, I am extending this exclusive opportunity to acquire it for $10000. Please let me know if you would like to proceed with this offer.
